item.title: Radian Laser
item.description: Radian is a small startup company that sells Laser Engravers and Cutters. I managed four projects for Radian that included two Web applications for control and calibration of the lasers. I also took over develop and maintanance of the Laser Engraver firmaware and Fleet Management project.
